alls easily, is simple to use, and there’s no lag either which makes it fantastic for gaming. And it works with <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.codeweavers.com/compatibility&amp;xcust=1-1-1661936-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">thousands of different titles</a> too so chances are good it’ll work for your specific application. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to take your Mac to the next level? Then there’s no time like the present. That’s because a <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/crossover-for-mac-1-yr-subscription?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=crossover-for-mac-1-yr-subscription&amp;utm_term=scsf-566895&amp;utm_content=a0x1P0000058W7IQAU&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-1661936-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">one-year subscription to CrossOver+</a> is discounted to just $49 for a limited time. Plus they have versions available for <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/crossover-for-linux-1-yr-subscription?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=crossover-for-linux-1-yr-subscription&amp;utm_term=scsf-567290&amp;utm_content=a0x1P0000058W7IQAU&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-1661936-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Linux</a> and <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/crossover-for-chromeos-1-yr-subscription?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=crossover-for-chromeos-1-yr-subscription&amp;utm_term=scsf-567291&amp;utm_content=a0x1P0000058W7IQAU&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-1661936-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Chrome OS</a> too so you can run the same software on all your systems regardless of your preference in operating systems.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a 